{"tid":1590103,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，我真係好想同勇武割蓆","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T18:10:26.000Z","uid":318047,"like":46,"dislike":411,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"d286d936c8ba435a8335a6af2af92245ae1db0be","tid":1590103,"uid":318047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"7，8月時嘅勇武我好尊敬<br />\n但係依幾日令我好無奈，甚至好嬲<br />\n好想講，勇武嘅行為開始變到同白衫同黑警冇咩分別<br />\n<br />\n一句 核彈都唔割<br />\n就好似政府被逼支持狗察一樣<br />\n依家和理非都被逼唔可以割蓆<br />\n好似鬧下你都係二五仔咁<br />\n<br />\n我同意俾人打要還手自衞，<br />\n但係如果人地冇出手，只係因為佢「疑似」係藍絲廢老，仲要只係撕過文宣鬧過下人就主動圍毆佢<br />\n請問你地同721白衫有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n打爛黨鐵同商場 我想問除咗發洩到底有咩作用？<br />\n爭取緊五大訴求嘅邊一樣？<br />\n<br />\n一邊鬧新屋嶺啲狗用私刑<br />\n另一邊廂又鼓吹要私了<br />\n老實講我都開始精神分裂<br />\n<br />\n勇武你地成日都叫和理非支持你<br />\n咁請問你地幾時有尊重過和理非？<br />\n最近嘅遊行一次激烈過一次<br />\n搞到越嚟越少和理非想/敢出嚟<br />\n呢場運動嘅成功係和勇一齊前行締造出嚟，<br />\n勇武依家行得太前，根本騎劫咗場運動，<br />\n將原本對準政權嘅槍口轉變成群眾鬥群眾，變咗個人發洩<br />\n<br />\n希望你地知道，<br />\n和理非並唔係奉旨支持你地嫁<br />\n出嚟遊行嘅人數已經大幅減少咗<br />\n勇武派如果冇咗和理非支持就只係一班黑社會<br />\n再係咁只會係勇武同和理非一齊攬炒<br />\n<br />\n大家都講過，依場運動已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n不成功，便成仁<br />\n既然係咁我地更加應該冷靜諗清楚要做啲咩<br />\n而唔係下下俾情緒控制<br />\n<br />\n左膠上"},{"pid":"cc9a0303b6177878fc238331c29e954d0ae13b49","tid":1590103,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士及死難者<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係中共嘅紀念日落鳩佢面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj