By":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"不推文啦<br />\n<br />\n警犬扮左膠"},{"pid":"ed00174625681d1366b0b201e0c7b5325f410bb0","tid":1590103,"uid":218364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"你真係無撚腦，打廢老嗰啲好明顯係狗扮嘅，只係儲緊彈藥一次過爆黑幕咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e9c0fade41847b41fba5be95b50de196cdaf25","tid":1590103,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"P牌左膠 <br />\nBlock得"},{"pid":"5159f48a82ffdaa9fa30ae7088680c646f25039d","tid":1590103,"uid":81560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"念力抗共？？？"},{"pid":"0827758c07ede00ae2983f7c92e41e53c1cba1dc","tid":1590103,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"不推文 分化撚"},{"pid":"f6c1f6b07b29e6d40ebba44c66c4250768c418af","tid":1590103,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"blocked 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6c9f0030c3b79eb3ced65c48aaceda36e1aa1d","tid":1590103,"uid":212849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"樓主一開頭假扮黃絲再打一大段藍絲言論<br />\n<br />\n高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46e79eed7b46ef097afc211cc8ea577400ae665","tid":1590103,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"建議樓主睇多次鏗鏘集721<br />\n相信你諗法會改變"},{"pid":"3a19eb028b08f5b1fad4c67ff23a7906c9c24280","tid":1590103,"uid":207727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"On9 警察暗角踢9人夠唔割 叫yellow object 屌你割乜9 同路人應該係提醒而唔係割蓆 你割得蓆姐係你唔係同路人啦"},{"pid":"4eb62435d4515416dd99619a4cc9c611acead20f","tid":1590103,"